data.description: Welcome to an area where location matters.Amazing 3 Bedroom 2 bath home located in the serene environment of the Willow Lake Villas.Split floor plan,a traditional layout,efficient kitchen with walk in pantry,gas fireplace, formal dining room, Accent Walls,Large Primary Bedroom Suite with dual vanities, walk in closet and separate shower room. Screened Porch that leads to the backyard that offers privacy and views.Peaceful setting in this community making it an ideal choice to call HOME.Enjoy the close amenities to the downtown area of Prescott with convenient access to essential services. Natural surroundings, privacy, quiet and peaceful neighborhood to enjoy the beautiful setting and enjoy the nearby lakes, hiking, biking, kayaking or just bird watching. Enjoy the Prescott Lifestyle
